Posts.Content: Slight update...stopped by obgyn office to see/discuss prelim report.  Both breasts are equally dense; left dense has asymmetry that requires further evaluation.
Posts.Title: scared...called back for "routine follow up" after 1st ever mammogram

Posts.Content: Hi.  I had my 1st ever mammogram on Saturday (I turned 40 recently).  I found out yesterday that the mammogram is considered "incomplete" and they need more pics and possibly an ultrasound for my left breast.  They said not to panic (I have an anxiety disorder so there's no chance that I'm not panicking).  My f/u scan is tomorrow morning -- which is good that they gave me the 1st available even though I had 4-6weeks to reschedule.
